  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s just a red tomato with a silly hat, trying to be a cool tomb raider by rolling and jumping all over the maps. Help him find all the treasures in the abandoned alien base, or watch him die... in many painful ways. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Tomato Jones - Episode 3</i> is the exciting third installment in the fun-filled series, following <i>Tomato Jones</i> and <i>Tomato Jones 2</i>, both available on Steam.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/dd6e2a4351ef878f8af7b6314c2e58c2.poster.avif?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/dd6e2a4351ef878f8af7b6314c2e58c2.webm?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/dd6e2a4351ef878f8af7b6314c2e58c2.mp4?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/be6cff5c3d63d4479b46aa7c83ca4413.webp?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=29 /></span>It This physics-based puzzle/adventure game combines classic RPG platformer gameplay with the skill-driven style of ball-rolling games. Your goal is to collect all coins and the hidden golden artifact at the end of each level while avoiding various dangerous traps, obstacles, and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike its predecessors, this game is set in a sci-fi atmosphere, packed with humor and funny moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT'S NEW</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 beautiful and challenging sci-fi levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New dangerous traps... and DRONES!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mr. Jones talks to himself like a madman.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative camera movement and viewing angles that will test your nerves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new world map and areas to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial controller support (but I don’t recommend it!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect to see the message \"DS die count reached!\" way more often.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT'S OLD</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great-looking \"soft body\" tomato physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple funny hats to choose from, plus new additions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun soundtrack and SFX.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of ketchup. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Mine carts?! Of course!  ;)</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/314a1a94464485b8aed6bb6c4c9d8062.poster.avif?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/314a1a94464485b8aed6bb6c4c9d8062.webm?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/314a1a94464485b8aed6bb6c4c9d8062.mp4?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get ready to die... a lot.</strong> <i> </i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/be6cff5c3d63d4479b46aa7c83ca4413.webp?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=29 /></span><strong>Tomato Jones - Episode 3</strong> is the hardest of the three games, and I strongly recommend playing the first two as well the <strong>Tomato Jones</strong> and <strong>Tomato Jones 2</strong>.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s just a red tomato with a silly hat, trying to be a cool tomb raider by rolling and jumping all over the maps. Help him find all the treasures in the abandoned alien base, or watch him die... in many painful ways. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Tomato Jones - Episode 3</i> is the exciting third installment in the fun-filled series, following <i>Tomato Jones</i> and <i>Tomato Jones 2</i>, both available on Steam.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/dd6e2a4351ef878f8af7b6314c2e58c2.poster.avif?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/dd6e2a4351ef878f8af7b6314c2e58c2.webm?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/dd6e2a4351ef878f8af7b6314c2e58c2.mp4?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/be6cff5c3d63d4479b46aa7c83ca4413.webp?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=29 /></span>It This physics-based puzzle/adventure game combines classic RPG platformer gameplay with the skill-driven style of ball-rolling games. Your goal is to collect all coins and the hidden golden artifact at the end of each level while avoiding various dangerous traps, obstacles, and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike its predecessors, this game is set in a sci-fi atmosphere, packed with humor and funny moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT'S NEW</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 beautiful and challenging sci-fi levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New dangerous traps... and DRONES!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mr. Jones talks to himself like a madman.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative camera movement and viewing angles that will test your nerves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new world map and areas to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial controller support (but I don’t recommend it!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect to see the message \"DS die count reached!\" way more often.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT'S OLD</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great-looking \"soft body\" tomato physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple funny hats to choose from, plus new additions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun soundtrack and SFX.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of ketchup. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Mine carts?! Of course!  ;)</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/314a1a94464485b8aed6bb6c4c9d8062.poster.avif?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/314a1a94464485b8aed6bb6c4c9d8062.webm?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/314a1a94464485b8aed6bb6c4c9d8062.mp4?t=1727008009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get ready to die... a lot.</strong> <i> </i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/788890/extras/be6cff5c3d63d4479b46aa7c83ca4413.webp?t=1727008009\" width=600 height=29 /></span><strong>Tomato Jones - Episode 3</strong> is the hardest of the three games, and I strongly recommend playing the first two as well the <strong>Tomato Jones</strong> and <strong>Tomato Jones 2</strong>.</p>",
